question.title: Use of MySQL8Dialect for MySQL 9.1.0 correct?
question.body:
What is the correct Hibernate dialect for MySQL 9.1.0 set in the application.properties of a Java Spring application? For MySQL 8 I would have used org.hibernate.dialect.MySQL8Dialect, but it seems there is no org.hibernate.dialect.MySQL9Dialect. So far MySQL8Dialect seems to work with MySQL 9.1.0 (judging from running it and getting no errors).

EDIT 1: I use Spring Boot 3.4.1.
